## Success Metrics

### Leading (first 2 weeks)
- Dashboard opens and renders all four widgets without error on every load.
- You open it at least 4 of 5 weekday mornings in the first two weeks.
- Time from opening Cowork to feeling oriented drops below 60 seconds (self-reported).

### Lagging (first 30 days)
- You report reduced morning context-switching friction.
- Financial awareness check-ins increase (you proactively notice budget trends).
- Dashboard becomes the default session-start habit, referenced in session logs.

