## Tech Stack Notes

- Built as a Cowork HTML artifact using `window.cowork.callMcpTool` and `window.cowork.askClaude`.
- Financial data sourced from a JSON snapshot file written by a scheduled task that reads your financial source at [enter path to your financial source here] (spreadsheet, notes file, or app export). Fields to pull: TBD with you.
- Quote pool sourced from [enter path to your quotes file here] or stubbed inline for v1.
- Quote rotation keyed to `new Date().toDateString()` for stable daily anchoring.
- Project list read from [enter path to your projects directory here] via file tools.
- Briefing content pulled from session logs or scheduled task output at [enter path here].

